.IP "\(bu" 4
unlink
.Sp
Unlink (delete) the file represented by the IO::All object.
.Sp
\&\s-1NOTE:\s0 You can unlink a file after it is open, and continue using it
until it is closed.
.IP "\(bu" 4
unlock
.Sp
Release a lock from an object that used the \f(CW\*(C`lock\*(C'\fR method.
.IP "\(bu" 4
utime
